        "description": "VIRTUAL RENOVATION EXPERIENCE\nHome Restoration offers an immersive experience, featuring stunning graphics, realistic physics, and a soothing soundtrack that creates the perfect ambiance for an enjoyable gameplay session.\n\nRENOVATE, REPAIR & CLEAN UP!\nThere are lots of houses waiting for you to renovate! Transform them from dilapidated ruins into stunning dream homes. Dive into the exciting world of renovation, fixing everything from broken pipes to damaged walls. Clean up rooms and sell unnecessary items for profit.\n\nDECORATE LIKE AN INTERIOR DESIGNER\nPersonalize each room with a vast selection of furniture, decor, and color schemes, allowing you to create a unique atmosphere that will leave potential buyers in awe. Additionally, enhance the aesthetics of your home by arranging the garden and introducing fresh blooms for a more appealing appearance.\n\nDISCOVER NEW CITIES\nFrom London to New York, there is a selection of 6 distinct cities where you can purchase and renovate new houses. Unlock these cities, and earn more money!",
